liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Caitlin Foord has a brace! Hayley Raso intercepts a poor clearance from the Philippines' goalkeeper, driving towards the top of the box and sending a cheeky little pass into the feet of Foord, who'd cut inside the box from the left. She takes a touch around her defender and fires into the far corner. 4-0.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 32' GOAL AUSTRALIA

children.content: Hayley Raso intercepts a poor clearance from the Philippines' goalkeeper, driving towards the top of the box and sending a cheeky little pass into the feet of Foord, who'd cut inside the box from the left.
She takes a touch around her defender and fires into the far corner.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: And it's Caitlin Foord's turn! Mary Fowler picks up the ball on the left, driving inside towards the top of the box before curling a stunning pass onto the chest of Sam Kerr, who's floating around the penalty spot. The skipper brings the ball down in a single touch and lays off for Foord, who's all alone to her left. And it's an easy-as-pie finish for the Arsenal forward. 3-0. Tony's having a grand old time.

Tony's having a grand old time.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: SAM KERR IS INEVITABLE! A stunning bit of individual dribbling from Caitlin Foord down the left sees her skip in behind two defenders before squaring for her captain, who's all alone near the penalty spot. All Kerr needs is a single touch to re-direct the pass into the far post. 2-0!
